claim.claim-text:
1. An apparatus for facilitating content selection at an electronic device, said apparatus comprising:
a content stream identifier configured to identify a set of content streams of a plurality of content streams having content available for play out at the electronic device;
a display configured to display an indication of each content stream of the set of content streams identified by said content stream identifier;
a monitor configured to detect selection of a displayed indication of a content stream displayed at said display;
wherein the content stream identifier is further configured to identify an updated set of content streams from the plurality of content streams, the updated set of content including content related to content played out in response to the selection of the displayed indication; and
wherein the display is further configured to display an indication of each content stream in the updated set of content streams.
